- It's a mission
to rescue Europe

00:29:37.960 --> 00:29:40.460
by stopping illegal immigration.

00:29:40.460 --> 00:29:42.970
We want to get a
crew, equip a boat,

00:29:42.970 --> 00:29:45.130
and set sails to
the Mediterranean

00:29:45.130 --> 00:29:47.990
to chase down these
